org.embulk.util.rubytime

Class RubyDateTimeParsedElementsQuery<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.embulk.util.rubytime.RubyDateTimeParsedElementsQuery<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TemporalQuery<Map<T,Object>>

    public final class RubyDateTimeParsedElementsQuery<T>
extends Object
implements TemporalQuery<Map<T,Object>>
    A query to retrieve a Map of parsed elements.

    The Map of parsed elements is analogous to a hash returned from Ruby's Date._strptime like below. 

    
 {:year=>2001, :mon=>2, :mday=>3}
    See Also:
    Ruby's Date._strptime
